lenders.loan_because: Microcredit is a concept developed by Muhammad Yunus, whom we work with. At Social Business Earth (SBE) we support this effective model to empower women and the poorest population on our planet so they can live a more dignified life.
lenders.occupational_info: Our mission is to spread and implement social business, a concept developed by Nobel Peace Laureate Muhammad Yunus, who chairs SBE's Advisory Board and officially recognizes us as a social business venture.
